  "title": "content creator cum video editor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>- Brainstorm and pitch engaging content</p>\n<p>- Manage social media accounts</p>\n<p>- Craft compelling captions for posts</p>\n<p>- Create simple graphic artwork</p>\n<p>- Simplify complex scientific concepts into clear, accurate, and compelling content.</p>\n<p>- Manage content calendars and ensure timely delivery across digital platforms.</p>\n<p>- Optimize content for social media, and audience engagement.</p>\n<p>- Track performance metrics and refine strategies based on data.</p>\n<p>- Assist with other ad-hoc marketing duties as required</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>- Diploma/Degree in Communications, Design, or related fields.</p>\n<p>- Min 1 year of content creation experience.</p>\n<p>- Proficiency in design tools and/or video editing.</p>\n<p>- Strong storytelling, writing, and organizational skills.</p>\n<p>- Basic social media knowledge.</p>",
